{"id":1027488568,"question_id":2904,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"9 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1692611090,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"10 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/1027488568/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sorting Three Groups","memory":"43.8 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public int minimumOperations(List<Integer> nums) {\n        // nums = [2,1,3,2,1]\n        // 1 : 1 4 0 2 3\n        // 2 : \n        // 3 : \n        \n        int len = nums.size();\n      \n        int[][] dp = new int[len+1][4]; // dp[i][j] 走到第i個數字的時候 最高位為j的最小cost\n        \n        // dp[i][1] = dp[i-1][1] + nums[i]!=1\n        // dp[i][2] = min(dp[i-1][1], dp[i-1][2]) + nums[i]!=2\n        // dp[i][3] = min(dp[i-1][1], dp[i-1][2], dp[i-1][3]) + nums[i]!=3\n        \n        \n        for(int i=1; i<=len; i++){\n         \n            dp[i][1] = dp[i-1][1] + (nums.get(i-1)!=1? 1 : 0);\n            dp[i][2] = Math.min( dp[i-1][1], dp[i-1][2]) + (nums.get(i-1)!=2? 1 : 0);\n            dp[i][3] = Math.min( dp[i-1][1], Math.min(dp[i-1][2], dp[i-1][3])) + (nums.get(i-1)!=3? 1 : 0);\n            \n        }\n        \n        int min = Integer.MAX_VALUE;\n        for(int i=1; i<=3; i++){\n            \n            min = Math.min(min, dp[len][i]);\n        }\n        \n        return min;\n        \n        \n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sorting-three-groups","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
